{"tid":15803,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台中機場去清境ge賤格共乘車公司","createTime":"2016-12-01T06:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T13:21:42.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc889cf1841d9a55cd73e55073deba0cfb5fa44","tid":15803,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"話說之前出發前上佢個網book共乘車<br />\n由台中機場去清境<br />\n佢俾我地㨂10點/12點/2點出發<br />\n我地揀咗12點<br />\n佢地都覆我ok<br />\n<br />\n我地11點半入境<br />\n入境大堂就見到好多人舉著塊紙牌<br />\n(應該都係共乘車d司機)<br />\n但搵來搵去都搵唔到我地個名<br />\n等到11點55分都唔見<br />\n就打電話問個間公司<br />\n佢話個司機on the way塞車<br />\n遲多少少<br />\n如是者 我地等到12點半 佢都未到<br />\n再打電話去追問<br />\n佢話個司機係清境來機場個程路塞車<br />\n叫我地食著lunch先<br />\n最後 個司機1點45分終於到啦<br />\n我見到張A4紙有我地個名<br />\n仲有另外2個唔識既人既名<br />\n咁我一開始覺得好合理<br />\n話哂係共乘車嘛<br />\n<br />\n於是一上車就問佢地係咪都等咗好耐<br />\n佢地話唔係 仲話岩岩落機無耐 (around 1點幾)<br />\n咁我覺得奇怪 如果佢地1點幾落機<br />\n點book 12點出發既共乘車?<br />\n佢地話佢地係book 2點出發既共乘車<br />\n<br />\n咁我明哂啦，即係因為12點出發得我地<br />\n個間公司想慳d錢出少架車<br />\n就要我地on99係機場等佢地2個鐘<br />\n等埋另外2個揀2點出發既人<br />\n仲要唔事先講我地知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我打電話去個間公司問佢<br />\n點解可以咁樣做?<br />\n我一早book 12點<br />\n如果唔夠客可以唔做我地生意<br />\n或者講個實況俾我知<br />\n等我決定等2個鐘，定係book過第二間<br />\n佢竟然話: <br />\n原先來接我地個司機真係塞車，<br />\n所以已經即時搵第二個司機接我地<br />\n<br />\n係去清境係路途中，我見到對面線完全無塞車<br />\n再者，如果真係臨時搵過另1個司機接我地<br />\n點解個司機會可以有一張用printer print出來既人名紙寫著我地個名? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你地想知多d，我再開名加post佢地個網既link! 等你地小心d!!"},{"pid":"2f2a7b9221602401d71551abd1767469a51466da","tid":15803,"uid":6908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:00:12.000Z","msg":"邊間？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">ok</span>便利店？"},{"pid":"23043b0b0046c09667f0bb3443985cc6e4ac09ba","tid":15803,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"佢講個個原因係有可能ge<br />\n不過好細囉😂"},{"pid":"308c8304b36b6274c181b6e3283592c19b3e5ba2","tid":15803,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢講個個原因係有可能ge<br />\n不過好細囉😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可能囉<br />\n個司機係有一張用printer print出來既人名紙<br />\n寫齊我地2group人既人名<br />\n架車上面又無printer<br />\n點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45f6fac2e84b78d01c0c0664f382b3a43c5cd04","tid":15803,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:06:27.000Z","msg":"某啲台灣人同大陸人冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2250f5cd18d77c984092b1c406630a0e02cf79","tid":15803,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"f1090bc0bf3360e5fa6a626fc89b83197945b733","tid":15803,"uid":37752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"post 聽日就去"},{"pid":"15ddcf096faadf3c673116d0d5a751456f709cb4","tid":15803,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"現場有冇都係共乘既司機摟生意？<br />\n如果有價又ok其實可以接受喎<br />\n鬼叫佢遲到（無論咩原因遲就係遲）<br />\n<br />\n利申未遇過我去親都係自己的返市區算"},{"pid":"7afed6fe22d830b67951b1a4f4368af1cf7ba0bd","tid":15803,"uid":23293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>某啲台灣人同大陸人冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主呢個算係咁,<br />\n有啲直情話燒咗啦, 自己搞掂啦!"},{"pid":"6a90bba33f5f5faf4efe3bebcd0d9eb1de93888e","tid":15803,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現場有冇都係共乘既司機摟生意？<br />\n如果有價又ok其實可以接受喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地要事先係香港入錢去中銀俾deposit<br />\n<br />\n所以就算佢地遲到 我地要硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702ce0c6f00404059e4c93a9332ff308f9025c22","tid":15803,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"開名啦咁賤格"},{"pid":"302fc004f17d3bb541786841e7c12bb4b0a2a5a1","tid":15803,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>現場有冇都係共乘既司機摟生意？<br />\n如果有價又ok其實可以接受喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地要事先係香港入錢去中銀俾deposit<br />\n<br />\n所以就算佢地遲到 我地要硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會平好多？我未試過。<br />\n<br />\n我上次係台中車站坐左架貴既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接開價600 （台中車站去機場）<br />\n我唔想浪費時間就照坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfe453a267da07e7cb49779616a99a9c3bff369","tid":15803,"uid":6060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"留名，利申一月頭去台中"},{"pid":"c25491a93cb70ef66dec269719aff8e36c261b86","tid":15803,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:41:17.000Z","msg":"我上次去都係坐果度即仲買飛去共同車上去，係耐d不過當睇風境，我記得係機場就有得坐"},{"pid":"e5c8a9958a60342f7f00941a3ef04407bf98fe5a","tid":15803,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上次去都係坐果度即<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">場</span></span>買飛去共同車上去，係耐d不過當睇風境，我記得係機場就有得坐</blockquote>"},{"pid":"57ed91b927180b1ae71a78b6d65b02ca87e9a736","tid":15803,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:52:21.000Z","msg":"三年前同女朋友又係去清境，女朋友出發前已經上網book定車由台中機場去清境，同埋已經交代哂咩航班同姓名。因為出發前一日打風，所以班機delay 2個鐘先起飛。四點幾落機，但間公司no show，屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後去左機場information desk幫手先搵到共乘車去清境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c4b4d679d65576cb39e1253b071825a023a6cb","tid":15803,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"台中來回清境好少會塞<br />\n<br />\n埔里至台中有高速路有普通路，either way都係相差30分鐘路程而已<br />\n<br />\n而清境到埔里，因為係山路，一塞就兩邊塞<br />\n<br />\n況且，冇理由塞完第二架車快過你第一架囉"}]}